{"tid":1311861,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"細佬脫毒計劃","createTime":"2019-07-13T11:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T04:46:38.000Z","uid":88084,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8d8ee799232a0702625bded5d8d1a27cb5f9d880","tid":1311861,"uid":88084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:13:10.000Z","msg":"小弟雖然未到男神級，但都係我嗰科系草，每個月keep住有人送禮物整野食話要追我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明我咁charm，偏偏我細佬係大毒男，可以幾日唔出街齋打機訓教嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆老母都話無咩願望，只希望我做大佬可以照顧細佬一世，將來成家立室留番間房俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗兩老心願，我決定今年要幫佢脫毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無人可以教我點樣幫細佬脫毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我知道細佬你都有上連登，希望你見到會生性喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60f0eb7ea04b62b3bff550daf78bc2befd6794f","tid":1311861,"uid":258566,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:14:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8cb8a50cbbfcf16e26ed03c388668f937067eb6","tid":1311861,"uid":190066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17df2fe08c236a1b5c124622fbf10eae6a2aeea6","tid":1311861,"uid":88084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:03:02.000Z","msg":"pishhhhhh"},{"pid":"e6bd8ae78a935046ede9038d4d143c0f0c21a87b","tid":1311861,"uid":88084,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:03:31.000Z","msg":"我細佬其實係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64720acfeba46c87c0d1432fccc4e295184d8e47","tid":1311861,"uid":88084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f60f0eb7ea04b62b3bff550daf78bc2befd6794f","tid"