係系草，咁外表上你都應該識打理，咁你幫下你細路執執個look，自然會有人approach 架喇<br />\n打機睇動漫果d冇問題架喎我又覺得，佢可以搵番個同佢有一樣興趣嘅伴侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebd478c2d92ddc72852444f6197896dd508ae4e","tid":1311861,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:39:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77d05660b57f5b0326bac5811b3971aa4a2bc0e6","tid":1311861,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:46:03.000Z","msg":"以毒攻毒....<br />\n搵日同你細佬講帶佢去木葉忍者村修練, 帶佢去新界啲森林"},{"pid":"d4cf225530c7150bd17fed34274cc1c7bc45b151","tid":1311861,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:46:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">以下係反擊黑警既文宣材料<br />\n示威者被補過百人，但到今日都無一個黑警被拘捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請永恆廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，令人明白抗爭者暴力反抗都係出師有名：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y7uAQAj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy7uAQAj.gif&h=7764e468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名少年於金鐘一帶背向警察站立，遭十多名速龍小隊成員強行拉扯到地上用警棍圍毆。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f6tuaAD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff6tuaAD.gif&h=1dcd33da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名少女下午於立法會地下門外落單，遭近十名警員以盾牌及警棍按倒地上瘋狂圍毆。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2BksGHv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2BksGHv.gif&h=e616484c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名手無寸鐵市民於大會堂對出方向，遭4-5名警員揮棍不停攻擊頭部倒地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6fwoV4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6fwoV4.gif&h=892ec315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名外藉男子於愛丁堡廣場附近，因行動不便獨自坐於花槽旁，遭警員以胡椒噴劑近距離向臉部射擊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L5kz59v.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL5kz59v.gif&h=6e4c68e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eNTYOnQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeNTYOnQ.gif&h=2d6b3e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nr0gz2S.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnr0gz2S.gif&h=f6419a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下午時份於金鐘天橋附近一帶，一名中年婦人向警員哭求停止對香港人使用武力，遭警員近距離以不明武器擊中頭部。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5KBLtok.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5KBLtok.gif&h=b8ae447c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一名市民於金鐘橋底下，遭警員以布袋彈瞄準頭部射擊。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h6jQEvO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh6jQEvO.gif&h=54b6b60a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n警員向示威者投擲鐵通。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gS1GMaW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgS1GMaW.jpg&h=07ae5fa1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n男警強脫女示威者上衣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E0Lz6a5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE0Lz6a5.gif&h=34338ba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員不斷挑釁示威者。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nMOxSRw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnMOxSRw.png&h=3bc0c0bf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n不合理搜身程序及罰企式羞辱年青人。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其他圖集</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ADpQExp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FADpQExp.png&h=8b63eed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PEsOrcs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPEsOrcs.gif&h=182c1c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真仆街 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n短片系列<br />\n香港警察粗暴對待示威者實錄<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nYV52IBKbtY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnYV52IBKbtY&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=78ca303c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nYV52IBKbtY</a><br />\n\t<br />\n示威者吐血<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhRCPds07zSM&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=41202185\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM</a><br />\n\t<br />\n拖行暈倒示威者<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGfhHJqNVPig&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=03b2183c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig</a><br />\n\t<br />\n唔比救護車入<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmT8SH2EJctk&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=457310c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk</a><br />\n\t<br />\n地鐵站噴椒<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsQk9mLw07WM&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=3eac4a48\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM</a><br />\n\t<br />\n開槍<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9bbFANmVWZ4&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=2879f8ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4</a><br />\n\t<br />\n向記者放tear gas<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcWZ0R67V5Yg&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=73105ebb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg</a><br />\n\t<br />\n向外國記者舉槍<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iTIqDFPjypU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=ht